		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Montgomery</placeName> <date>Decb. 6 &#8220;48</date></p>
				<p>The Chefra Mef. Cholim</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">to <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee> &#8220; <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Dear Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">We send you<lb/> enclosed Three Dollars for the Occident from<lb/> last year&#44; and you will please direct<lb/> the Same the next time to</p>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><persName role="author">Mrss J &#38; G Myer</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(7)"><placeName>Montgy. Ala</placeName></p>
				<p>About our Chefra we have to write you&#44;<lb/> that she is going on very well&#44; we have<lb/> now <add>Hebrew</add> <add>&#8220;Beit Hakvachot&#8221; JE transliteration</add>&#44; and have rented<lb/> a Synagogue&#44; also the Election of<lb/> our Officers took place on the <date>5th of<lb/> November 48</date>.  and it is elected</p>
				<list type="ordered">
				<head></head>
				<item n="1"><persName>Jacob Myer</persName> President</item>
				<item n="2"><persName>P. Krans</persName>&#44; Vice president</item>
				<item n="3"><persName>Emanuel Lehman</persName>&#44; Secretary</item>
				<item n="4"><persName>Henry Weil</persName>&#44; Treasurer</item>
				<item n="5"><persName>M. Englander</persName>&#44; Trustee</item>
				<item n="6"><persName>Charles Levy</persName>&#44; <add>&#63;</add></item>
				</list>
				<p>Please inset this in your next Occident&#44;<lb/> and write me please an <sic>answere</sic>&#44; &#38;<lb/> by so doing we are respectf.</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)">The President</p>
			<p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">J Myer</persName>   <persName>Em. Lehman</persName></p>
				<p rend="align(right)">Secret&#58;</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(6)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
